# Academic Mentorship Platform — Project Context

## Project Overview

MentorHub is a full-stack Academic Mentorship Platform connecting students with professional mentors for technical guidance, code reviews, career advice, and learning support.

Session Duration:

* 45 minutes

User Roles:

* Student
* Mentor
* Admin

Backend:

* REST API already exists
* Authentication implemented
* Student APIs implemented
* Mentor APIs implemented
* Session APIs implemented
* Admin APIs implemented
* Technical Stack APIs implemented
* Mentor Approval APIs implemented
* AI Audit APIs implemented

The frontend should be designed around the existing backend.

